This paper is primarily focused on security log analysis and incident response, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the challenges of processing large volumes of data, which could be related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of GPUs for log processing is a key aspect of the paper, which could be relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
